article_title: ACA Marketplace CEO tours Coast enrollment sites
article_text: BILOXI -- With the open enrollment deadline for health-care insurance looming, Kevin Counihan, CEO of the Federal Marketplace for the Affordable Care Act, was on the Coast on Tuesday to tour several enrollment sites.
